chunks.html_content:
Contact Companies House if you need help with tasks including:

  • registering your company
  • filing your confirmation statement (previously annual return)
  • filing your company accounts
  • telling them about changes to your company, such as directors joining or leaving
  • closing a company
  • finding information about a company
  • complaining about a company

If you send a letter, email or document to Companies House, include:

  • the full name of the company you’re enquiring about
  • the company number if registered - find information about a company

heading_context: British Sign Language (BSL) video relay service
chunks.html_content:
To use the BSL video relay service you must:

  • first check you can use the service

  • go to the video relay service

The video relay service uses a free plugin. You may need to change the security settings on your device to install this.
chunks.plain_content:
Contact Companies House
British Sign Language (BSL) video relay service
To use the BSL video relay service you must:

  
    first check you can use the service
  
  
    go to the video relay service
  

The video relay service uses a free plugin. You may need to change the security settings on your device to install this.

chunks.html_content: You can also write to Companies House, but you’ll usually get a faster response by calling or sending an email.
